  waste-management category page was used instead to find a fresh listing.
- During prospect-evaluation, BizBuySell and DealStream returned HTTP 403 to subagent
  automated fetch; evaluations relied on the Playwright-validated extracts + screenshots
  captured in the main run plus other public sources.
- Airtable Industry Match field has no Printing / Medical / Marketing options — 6 leads
  tagged "Other"; true NAICS stored in the NAICS Code field and Notes.
